#META# Genres: Medicine
#META# Type: Translation
#META# Translator: Ḥunayn ibn Isḥāq or Ḥubayš ibn al-Ḥasan
#META# Translated from: Syriac (close)
#META# Date: between 850 and 890
#META# Ed_info: Mattock, John N. and Lyons, Malcolm C. (1969b), Kitāb Buqrāṭ fī l-amrāḍ al-bilādiyya. Hippocrates :: On Endemic Diseases (Airs, Waters and Places) (W. Heffer and Sons 5), W. Heffer and Sons, Cambridge, vol. 5, pp. 1-163

